# Per-stack config (Pulumi.<stack>.yaml) holds environment-specific settings and
# any encrypted secrets; the Pulumi Cloud backend is the source of truth. Only
# the project file (Pulumi.yaml) is committed.
Pulumi.*.yaml
!Pulumi.yaml

# Compiled Pulumi program binary left behind by a manual `go build .` (named
# after the module's last path element).
/repo_config
/pulumi
